<h3>Special price countdown</h3>
<p class="indent">The given module allows to display the timer of discount expiration for special products.<br>
You can enable/disable the module via Magento Admin Panel, in <strong>System > Configuration > Templatemonster > Special Price Countdown</strong> section.</p>
<figure class="img-polaroid"><img src="img/magento/countdown.jpg" alt="" /></figure>
<p class="indent">In order to edit the appearance of the timer, you need to edit the <strong>flipclock.css (flipclock.less)</strong> file located in the <strong>skin/frontend/default/themeXXX/css/tm/specialpricecountdown</strong> folder.<p>
		